        <text><![CDATA[<p>This resolution supports the recognition of Distracted Driving Awareness Month.</p><p>The resolution also supports the efforts of the Department of Transportation, state and local governments, and state and local law enforcement to prevent and stop distracted driving.</p>]]></text>
